code: "use strict";export function memoize(callback){let previous;let result;return(...dependencies)=>{let hasChanged=false;if(previous){if(previous.length!==dependencies.length){hasChanged=true;}else{for(let i=0;i<previous.length;i++){if(previous[i]!==dependencies[i]){hasChanged=true;break;}}}}else{hasChanged=true;}previous=dependencies;if(hasChanged||result===undefined){result=callback(...dependencies);}return result;};}
